ActCanadian Environmental Protection Act, 1999
Department of Fisheries and Oceans Act
SubjectEnvironmental Occurrences Notification Agreement ON, MB, BC, SK, AB, Yukon
PrecisOrder approving that the Minister of the Environment and the Minister of Fisheries and Oceans enter into the ENVIRONMENTAL OCCURRENCES NOTIFICATION AGREEMENTS between the Government of Canada and the Governments of Ontario, Manitoba, British Columbia, Yukon, Saskatchewan and Alberta, in order to establish a streamlined notification system for persons required to notify proncial/territorial and federal governments of an environmental occurrence.
